@node usage "USAGE"

 FroggerNG_GUI can be started from both CLI and WB (icon).

 @{u}Options:@{uu}

 TEMPLATE:
   DRAGBAR=DB/S,NOBOTTOM=NOBT/S,NOFROGQUIT=NOFQ/S,HIDE/K/N,RUNFROG=RF/S,VPSFIX/S:

 DRAGBAR:
   Enables window's dragbar

 NOBOTTOM:
   Disables automatic placing GUI under Frogger's window

 NOFROGQUIT:
   Quit GUI dosen't mean quit Frogger

 HIDE:
   Sets time (in seconds) to hide GUI's window.
   Default 7, 0 disables option.

 RUNFROG:
   Frogger starts with GUI.
   ***************************************************
   * For using this option first you have to edit    *
   * rexx/runfrog.rexx file (change path to Frogger) *
   ***************************************************

 VPSFIX:
   Try to use this option if you use VisualPrefs and you
   have wrong FroggerNG_CP window size.


 @{u}ToolTypes:@{uu}

 All options available from CLI, are also available as tooltypes.
 (take a look at FroggerNG_GUI icon)


 @{u}Keyboard:@{uu}

 ESC, q       - Quit GUI (and FroggerNG)
 [            - Volume down
 ]            - Volume up
 +, =         - Zoom in
 -            - Zoom out

@endnode

